com.rublon.sdk.common.html

Class ConsumerScript

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rublon.sdk.common.html.ConsumerScript

  • public class ConsumerScript
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for generating the HTML script tag that embeds consumer's JavaScript library. The so-called "consumer script" is an individualized JavaScript library that allows the website to use Rublon JavaScript elements - usually the Rublon GUI. The library searches Rublon button HTML containers in the website's DOM tree and fills them with proper content.
